verbs.description: Women [V: are] dancing on tables . And Rudy Giuliani is right there with them , swinging a white napkin while dining at a restaurant in Jerusalem on Wednesday during a tour through Israel to speak to the Globes Capital Market Conference and to meet with Jerusalem Mayor Nir Barkat . The former New York City mayor 's recent trip has sparked headlines duirng the trip for comments about everything from President Trump 's planned summit with North Korean leader Kim Jong Un to Stormy Daniels .
